  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/c8d45ff11c68fe19f18a47d4167c673d.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/9db9f7b5080e58d4bb028165d57fd1be.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>\"The Temple of Discipline dedicated to Undiana, the Goddess of Discipline...<br>However, in the goddess' indifference, they disappeared one by one.\"<br><br>\"And here in Andalun, the last remaining temple of order was also<br>dying its light due to the undead from the tomb of the traitors.\"<br><br>\"From now on, everything will be their end...\"<br><br>Claire, the last remaining priest, decides to risk life with the soldiers<br>to fight against the undead for the safe evacuation of the villagers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/e570bd8f247c04dd5d8638566d06e27c.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>The offensive of the undead begins.<br>Gather holy power to summon soldiers and strengthen the starlight of Hellendil to defeat the undead.<br>If the undead destroy this place, it will be game over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/ee958ac52b50467d14339e2743b358df.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>▷ Charming characters<br>▷ Character Tower Defense<br>▷ Game Mode: Story Mode, Endless Mode<br>▷ Various skins and specials that can be unlocked while playing<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/7f23464e72b4783cee1f8a0072c47681.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=400 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/c8d45ff11c68fe19f18a47d4167c673d.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/9db9f7b5080e58d4bb028165d57fd1be.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>\"The Temple of Discipline dedicated to Undiana, the Goddess of Discipline...<br>However, in the goddess' indifference, they disappeared one by one.\"<br><br>\"And here in Andalun, the last remaining temple of order was also<br>dying its light due to the undead from the tomb of the traitors.\"<br><br>\"From now on, everything will be their end...\"<br><br>Claire, the last remaining priest, decides to risk life with the soldiers<br>to fight against the undead for the safe evacuation of the villagers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/e570bd8f247c04dd5d8638566d06e27c.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>The offensive of the undead begins.<br>Gather holy power to summon soldiers and strengthen the starlight of Hellendil to defeat the undead.<br>If the undead destroy this place, it will be game over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/ee958ac52b50467d14339e2743b358df.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>▷ Charming characters<br>▷ Character Tower Defense<br>▷ Game Mode: Story Mode, Endless Mode<br>▷ Various skins and specials that can be unlocked while playing<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/7f23464e72b4783cee1f8a0072c47681.avif?t=1747123601\" width